-- U.S.'s Thad Allen Says Seep Detected `a Distance' From BP's Gulf Oil Well
-- Jeran Wittenstein
-- 2010-07-19T00:55:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/u-s-s-thad-allen-says-seep-detected-a-distance-from-bp-s-gulf-oil-well.html

          
          
             U.S. Admiral Thad Allen said a seep
has been detected ‘a distance’ from the Macondo oil well in the
Gulf of Mexico.  
 Allen commented in a letter sent today to BP Plc’s Chief
Managing Director Bob Dudley.  
          
          


  


        